When you are catering an event, catering too much or too little can always be a concern. This guide by Food and Home on catering quantities are typical portion sizes you can serve per person and will ensure that your guests will not leave your dinner party or event hungry.  Read the original story on Food and Home. Roast leg of lamb with mint and pomegranate rubies  Heirloom tomato tart  Pork roast with cranberry caramelised green apples and sage 